import React, { useState, useEffect, useRef } from "react"; import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; import { Button } from "@mui/material/Button"; import styles from "./Header.module.scss"; import Container from "@mui/material/Container"; import logo from "../../media/logo/logo.png"; import user from "../../media/header/auth-like-menu/user.png"; import like from "../../media/header/auth-like-menu/like.png"; import menu from "../../media/header/auth-like-menu/menu.png"; import tg from "../../media/header/socials/tg.png"; import youtube from "../../media/header/socials/youtube.png"; import vk from "../../media/header/socials/vk.png"; import down_arrow from "../../media/header/down-arrow.png"; import art_city_logo from "../../media/projects/art-city/logo.png"; import art_city_landscape from "../../media/projects/art-city/landscape.png"; export const Header = () => { const isAuth = false; const onClickLogout = () => {}; const [isOpen, setIsOpen] = useState(false); // Состояние для отслеживания открытия/закрытия меню const toggleMenu = () => { setIsOpen(!isOpen); // Переключение состояния открытия/закрытия }; const [headerHeight, setHeaderHeight] = useState(0); const [navWidth, setNavWidth] = useState(0); const headerRef = useRef(null); const navRef = useRef(null); useEffect(() => { // Устанавливаем начальные размеры хедера и навигации if (headerRef.current) { setHeaderHeight(headerRef.current.offsetHeight); } if (navRef.current) { setNavWidth(navRef.current.offsetWidth); } // Обновляем размеры при изменении окна const handleResize = () => { if (headerRef.current) { setHeaderHeight(headerRef.current.offsetHeight); } if (navRef.current) { setNavWidth(navRef.current.offsetWidth); } }; window.addEventListener("resize", handleResize); return () => { window.removeEventListener("resize", handleResize); }; }, []); return ( <>
